Name: Da! Russian Quiz
About the game: A quiz that helps you review words and phrases in Russian. Over 3,500 Advanced phrases, 350 Verbs, 1500 nouns and exactly 33 letters for all your learning efforts. Features All questions have a timer set between 2 and 20 seconds. Choose how many questions per quiz. From 3 to 30. The following levels are available: Cyrillic Alphabet, Basic phrases, Verbs, Nouns and Advanced phrases You can review any level (except for Advanced phrases) and even get a transliteration to help your learning. The questions can be either in English or Russian
